<figureCitation box="[285,358,1866,1891]" captionStart="FIGURES 19 – 26" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1302,1324]" captionTargetBox="[171,1428,481,1280]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[159,1428,481,1280]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 19 – 26. Male genitalia of Sertania gen. nov. species. 19 – 22, Sertania guttata comb. nov. from Punta de los Llanos, La Rioja, Argentina (ZUEC), lateral view (19), tegumen and uncus in dorsal view (20), tegumen and uncus in lateral view (21), valvae in lateral view (22). 23 – 24, Sertania jaibensis comb. nov., stat. nov. paratype from Diamantina, Minas Gerais, Brazil (DZUP), tegumen and uncus in lateral view (23), valvae in lateral view (24). 25 – 26, Sertania lambedor comb. nov., stat. nov. from Ibimirim, Pernambuco, Brazil (ZUEC), tegumen and uncus in lateral view (25), valvae in lateral view (26). Scale bars = 0.25 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/892883/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="173">25–26</figureCitation>
